messages.messageBody:
Hi,

I am a list owner of another email discussion list called
Texas Home Educators. May I ask a favor of you? Could you forward
this
information to your general topic list for any of your subscriber who
may be
in Texas. My desire in forming this list was to give those in Texas a
place for local information and political alerts. Here is an
introduction
and explanation of what our list encompasses:

This email-based discussion list is a list to serve the Home
Educators of Texas in discussions of home education styles, philosophy,
books, curriculum, events, and laws in a Christian atmosphere.
Although discussions will sometimes stray from the direct purpose, it
usually does not stray from our children's interests.

To subscribe email: TxHmEd-subscribe@...

If you are interested in Home Education in Texas, I hope you
will join us.

I hope this information is a blessing to you. If I can be
of any assistance to you, please do not hesitate to ask.

Jube
Texas Home Educators
Jube@...
